NG0801:1: sa ma ya i mam b+ha ling ta dgra bgegs la kha ram kha hi /
NG0801:3: pany+tsa a mr-i ta kha ram kha hi /
NG0801:4: de nas 'phrin las bcol ba ni /
NG0801:6: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NG0801:7: srog gi gshed du bskul ba ni //
NG0801:8: bdud rgyal thod pa'i 'phreng ba can //
NG0801:9: sku ni mthing nag chen po la //
NG0801:10: chibs su bdud rta nag po chibs //
NG0801:11: lcags mdung nag po g.yas na thogs //
NG0801:12: g.yon na thod pa'i 'phreng ba bgrang *//
NG0801:13: thod pa skam po'i dbu rgyan can //
NG0801:14: mi lpags rlon pa sku la gsol //
NG0801:15: rgyu ma sbrul gyis lus brgyan cing */
NG0801:16: khrag dang zhag gi thig le can //
NG0801:17: mche ba gtsigs shing gsus po che //
NG0801:18: tsit+ta'i khrag la longs spyod pas /
NG0801:19: khyod ni srog bdag chen po ste //
NG0801:20: sring cig rdo rje re ma ti //
NG0801:21: ming sring gnyis kyi dam bcas pa //
NG0801:22: dam bcas bzhin du phrin las mdzod //
NG0801:23: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kas //
NG0801:24: dbang rtags thod pa byin nas ni //
NG0801:25: bka' stsal dam phog mdzad pa'i tshe //
NG0801:26: de tshe khas blangs dam bcas pa //
NG0801:27: bsgrub mchog bskyang bar dam bcas shing *//
NG0801:28: dgra bo bsgral bar khas blangs pas //
NG0801:29: dam nyams bsgral pa'i dus la bab /
NG0801:30: khyod ni srog bdag chen po ste //
NG0801:31: dgra bo'i srog la mnga' thang mdzod //
NG0801:32: srog dbug long zhig sa ma ya //
NG0801:33: srog rtsa chod cig sa ma ya /
NG0801:34: khyod kyi zas skal khams gsum sha yin te //
NG0801:35: dam nyams sha ni zan du gsol //
NG0801:36: dgra bo'i sha la kha ram kha hi //
NG0801:38: khyod kyi skom ni skye 'gro'i khrag yin te //
NG0801:39: dgra bo'i khrag ni skom du gsol //
NG0801:40: dgra bo'i khrag la pi pa to //
NG0801:42: khyod ni dmag dpon chen po ste //
NG0801:43: sa gzhi thams cad dmag gis khengs //
NG0801:44: dgra bo'i yul du dmag 'dren gyis /
NG0801:45: dmag sna drongs shig thod 'phreng can //
NG0801:46: dmag gzhug rtul cig thod 'phreng can //
NG0801:47: go mtshon stor cig thod 'phreng can //
NG0801:48: dmag dpung bskyed la ru mtshon phyor //
NG0801:49: dgra bo'i yul du dmag drongs la //
NG0801:50: dam nyams dgra po'i bla mkhar shig / bla shing chod la bla rdo rkus //
NG0801:51: bla chu hub kyi thob la shog / khyod kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NG0801:52: dus la bab bo sa ma ya //
NG0801:53: ma g.yel bcol ba'i 'phrin las mdzod //
NG0801:54: de skad ces ni bskul bya ba //
NG0801:55: de nas pho nya rab bkye ba //
NG0801:56: shes pa ling ga dag la bstim //
NG0801:58: de yi thugs kyi sprul pa las //
NG0801:59: bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs chen ni //
NG0801:60: steng gi phyogs nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:61: bdud kyi rgyal po khro bdag 'bar ba rje //
NG0801:62: phyag na bdud kyi spar shad 'bar ba bsnams //
NG0801:63: steng gi phyogs nas dgra bo khug la shog /
NG0801:64: ma ra ya dzahdzah che ge mo ma ra na
NG0801:66: shar gyi phyogs nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:67: bdud kyi rgyal po ma ha khro bdag rje //
NG0801:68: phyag na bdud zhags nag po bsnams //
NG0801:69: shar gyi phyogs nas dgra bo khug la shog / hu~m /
NG0801:71: mtshams nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:72: bdud kyi rgyal po ti ti ti myag rje //
NG0801:73: phyag na bdud kyi gsod byed spu gri rnon po bsnams /
NG0801:74: shar lho mtshams nas dgra bo khug la shog / hu~m /
NG0801:75: lho yi phyogs nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:76: bdud kyi rgyal po khro bdag thod pa rje //
NG0801:77: phyag na bdud khram stag gi mgo can bsnams //
NG0801:78: lho yi phyogs nas dgra bo khug la shog / hu~m /
NG0801:79: lho nub mtshams nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:80: bdud kyi rgyal po dmu bdud brang dkar rje //
NG0801:81: phyag na shod kyi sgro ba mi 'gro can /
NG0801:82: khal du bong bu gwa pa lcags mthur can la bskyil //
NG0801:83: lho nub mtshams nas dgra bo khug la shog / hu~m /
NG0801:84: nub kyi phyogs nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:85: bdud kyi rgyal po tshangs pa bdud khro rje //
NG0801:86: phyag na bdud kyi dril zhags 'bar ba brnams //
NG0801:87: nub byang phyogs nas dgra bo khug la shog / hum /
NG0801:88: nub byang mtshams nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:89: bdud kyi rgyal po ting ri mgo ston rje //
NG0801:90: phyag na bdud sha nag po'i thod pa bsnams //
NG0801:91: nub byang mtshams nas dgra bo khug la shog hu~m /
NG0801:92: byang gi phyogs nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:93: bdud kyi rgyal po khro rje ru rgyal rje //
NG0801:94: phyag na bdud rta nag po mgo gcod bsnams //
NG0801:95: byang gi phyogs nas dgra bo khug la shog / hu~m /
NG0801:96: byang shar mtshams nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:97: bdud kyi rgyal po spyi bdud yam pa khro rje nag po rje //
NG0801:98: phyag na bdud kyi tr-i shul rtse gsum bsnams //
NG0801:99: byang shar mtshams bas dgra bo khug la shog / hu~m /
NG0801:100: 'og gi phyogs nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:101: bdud kyi rgyal po sa mdog nag po rje /
NG0801:102: phyag na chu srin phur pa gti mug phag mgo can //
NG0801:103: skyes 'gro thams cad gsod par byed //
NG0801:104: 'og gi phyogs nas dgra bo khug la shog / ma ra na dza dza /
NG0801:105: che ge mo ni ra ma ra ya rbad pu nan dza dza /
NG0801:106: zhes ni rbad de bla tshe dgug / bdud khros pa'i rgyud las /
NG0801:107: bstod bskul pho nya bdag pa'i le'u ste drug pa'o //  // yang dpal chen pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0801:108: lha rtags byung nas dgra rtags rnams //
NG0801:109: bul las de bag bul na //
NG0801:110: mi lus mo shing byang bu la //
NG0801:111: dril bu ste che dgu'i lcags la gzugs //
NG0801:112: de la thun gyis brabs te gsang *//
NG0801:113: mgo ba'i lha dang 'di yis dbye //
NG0801:114: 'bob dang khyi lud rwa ru dang *//
NG0801:115: zhabs ma gu gul za 'og bsregs //
NG0801:116: mtshan ma'i ming rus de la bdug / dgra lha pho lha yul lha dang *//
NG0801:117: mo lha srog lha rgyal po ste //
NG0801:118: rgyal rten phral la gsad par bya'o //
NG0801:120: spogs pa'i cho ga lha dang dbral ba'i le'u ste
NG0801:121: bdun pa'o // // de skad ces bka' stsal nas
NG0801:122: / dpa' bo chen po gtso bo dang 'khor ltar
NG0801:123: snang ba'i de nyid yang dag par mi snang bar
NG0801:124: / byas te / rtsa ba'i longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la thim ste /
NG0801:125: chos kyi sku dang tha mi dad par gyur to //
NG0801:126: zhal gcig phyag kyang gnyis pa ste //
NG0801:128: nyid kyang bstan pa bsrung ba'i don du nye bar 'khod de /
NG0801:129: legs nyes kyi gzu bo mdzad do //
NG0801:130: 'khor rnams kyang gtso bo la 'dud pa'i tshul gyis gnas par gyur to //
NG0801:131: dam nyams yud tsam gyis bkug nas //
